---
import LandingLayout from "../../layouts/LandingLayout.astro";
---

<LandingLayout
	title="Schematic"
	description="Filesystem routes with contracts, not vibes — lattice map and contracted code."
	slug="schematic"
>
	<main id="main" class="lp-schematic">
		<section class="hero" aria-label="Hero">
			<svg
				class="map"
				viewBox="0 0 1200 700"
				preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice"
				aria-hidden="true"
			>
				<path class="edge" d="M180 420 L420 280 L660 360" />
				<path class="edge" d="M420 280 L520 140 L780 180" />
				<path class="edge" d="M660 360 L820 480 L980 320" />
				<path class="edge" d="M520 140 L660 360 L820 480" />
				<circle class="node" cx="180" cy="420" r="8" />
				<circle class="node lit" cx="420" cy="280" r="9" />
				<circle class="node" cx="520" cy="140" r="8" />
				<circle class="node lit" cx="660" cy="360" r="9" />
				<circle class="node" cx="820" cy="480" r="8" />
				<circle class="node" cx="780" cy="180" r="7" />
				<circle class="node lit" cx="980" cy="320" r="8" />
				<text x="150" y="455">route</text>
				<text x="390" y="255">schema</text>
				<text x="500" y="120">middleware</text>
				<text x="640" y="395">handler</text>
				<text x="800" y="515">response</text>
				<text x="760" y="160">openapi</text>
				<text x="960" y="300">check</text>
			</svg>

			<div class="hero-copy">
				<div class="brand-mark">
					<img src="/favicon.svg" alt="" width="40" height="40">
					Routa
					<span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
				</div>
				<h1 class="headline">Filesystem routes with contracts, not vibes</h1>
				<p class="lede">
					A schematic of the API: routes as edges, schemas as nodes, OpenAPI as projection. Category
					claim first — then the proof below.
				</p>
				<div class="cta-row">
					<a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://routa-ts.dev/docs/">Get started</a>
					<a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://github.com/Routa-ts/Routa">GitHub</a>
				</div>
				<div class="cli" data-cmd="pnpm create routa-ts@latest">
					<span>$ pnpm create routa-ts@latest</span>
					<button type="button">Copy</button>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="section-inner">
				<p class="section-kicker">Side by side</p>
				<h2 class="section-title">Untyped handler vs contracted route</h2>
				<p class="section-lede">
					Same job. One hopes the status codes match the docs. The other declares the contract in
					source.
				</p>
				<div class="compare">
					<div class="code-panel">
						<div class="code-panel__bar"><span>without Routa</span><span>vibes</span></div>
						<pre
						><code>app.post(<span class="str">"/users"</span>, <span class="kw">async</span> (c) => {"{"}
  <span class="kw">const</span> body = <span class="kw">await</span> c.req.json();
  <span class="cm">// validate… somewhere?</span>
  <span class="kw">const</span> user = <span class="kw">await</span> create(body);
  <span class="kw">return</span> c.json(user, <span class="str">201</span>);
{"}"});</code></pre>
					</div>
					<div class="code-panel">
						<div class="code-panel__bar"><span>with Routa</span><span>contract</span></div>
						<pre
						><code><span class="kw">export default</span> <span class="fn">defineRoute</span>({"{"}
  post: <span class="fn">createRoute</span>({"{"}
    input: {"{"} body: CreateUserSchema {"}"},
    responses: {"{"}
      success: {"{"} status: <span class="str">201</span>, schema: UserSchema {"}"},
    {"}"},
    run: <span class="kw">async</span> ({"{"} input, ctx {"}"}) =>
      users.createUser(input.body, ctx),
  {"}"}),
{"}"});</code></pre>
					</div>
				</div>
				<ul class="pillars" style="margin-top: 2.5rem">
					<li>
						<strong>Route = contract</strong>
						<p>Path, methods, I/O, and outcomes in one file.</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Lattice composition</strong>
						<p>Middleware and schemas form a typed graph you can check.</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>OpenAPI peer</strong>
						<p>Projection of the same lattice — scaffold or emit.</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>CLI lifecycle</strong>
						<p>check, build, start — in that order.</p>
					</li>
				</ul>
				<ul class="built-on" style="margin-top: 2rem">
					<li>Hono</li>
					<li>Zod</li>
					<li>OpenAPI</li>
					<li>TypeScript</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="v0-note"><strong>v0</strong> — diagrammatic, not cosmic. No fake logos.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="close">
			<div class="close-inner">
				<div>
					<h2>Map the docs</h2>
					<p>From first route to OpenAPI lockstep.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="cta-row">
					<a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://routa-ts.dev/docs/start/quickstart/"
						>Quickstart</a
					>
					<a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/landings/">All options</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</LandingLayout>
